<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/styles/main.css" />
  <title>Privacy Policy - Taskify</title>
  <style>
    .privacy-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 100px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .privacy-container h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #9900f8;
    }
    .privacy-container h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 32px 0 12px;
    }
    .privacy-container p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .back-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: #9900f8;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .back-btn:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .lang-btn {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      background-color: #9900f8;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- 语言切换按钮 -->

  <div class="privacy-container">
    <a href="/" class="back-btn" data-i18n="privacy.back">← Back to Home</a>
    <button id="lang-toggle" class="lang-btn">中文</button>
    <h1 data-i18n="privacy.title">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.intro_heading">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.intro_text">Welcome to Taskify. We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy.</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.collect_heading">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.collect_text">We collect information you provide directly to us, such as your name, email address, and password when you create an account.</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.use_heading">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.use_text">We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services, and to communicate with you.</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.cookies_heading">4. Cookies</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.cookies_text">We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to track activity on our service.</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.storage_heading">5. Local Storage</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.storage_text">Taskify uses browser local storage to save your preferences and session data.</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.security_heading">6. Data Security</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.security_text">We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information.</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="privacy.contact_heading">7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p data-i18n="privacy.contact_text">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: privacy@taskify.com</p>
  </div>

  <script src="../static/i18n.js"></script>
</body>
</html>